      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It honestly breaks my heart a little to even think about parting with this beauty, but it's time for my pride and joy to find a new home. I\u2019ve absolutely pampered this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-ready condition. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' magic. Aside from maybe a tiny bit of dust from sitting in the garage, she\u2019s perfect. Come on over, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I'm so proud of this one!",
