    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously sorted E92 platform that redefines the standard for a turn-key enthusiast machine. This specimen features a high-revving power plant with a perfectly linear torque curve, recently optimized via a comprehensive top-end refresh including recalibrated throttle actuators and a precision carbon-cleaning service. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by high-rebound dampening and reinforced subframe bushings, effectively neutralizing lateral deflection during high-G cornering. We\u2019ve managed the unsprung weight with forged alloys, while the titanium valved exhaust system ensures optimal backpressure and a visceral acoustic profile. Every fluid has been flushed with high-temp synthetics, and the short-throw shifter provides a mechanical, bolt-action engagement that is increasingly rare. This isn't just a driver\u2019s car; it\u2019s a precision-engineered instrument maintained to exceed factory tolerances. Zero hesitation, no parasitic power loss\u2014just raw, mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
