    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step back into an era of effortless elegance with this breathtaking masterpiece. Clad in a finish that captures the moonlight, this machine isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule. Inside, the scent of rich, preserved leather greets you like an old friend, while the dash\u2014unmarred by time\u2014glows with the warmth of genuine walnut. When the engine stirs, it doesn't just start; it exhales a low, confident purr that speaks of open highways and coastal sunsets. This is more than a vehicle; it is a statement of grace, ready to carry you into your next great adventure.",
      "price": 43500.0,
